title: Palestine Producer Prices Change
description: Producer Prices in Palestine increased 1.78 percent in September of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Producer Prices Change in Palestine averaged 1.31 percent from 2012 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 12 percent in March of 2022 and a record low of -6.30 percent in May of 2020. Producer prices change refers to year over year change in price of goods and services sold by manufacturers and producers in the wholesale market during a given period. This page provides - Palestine Producer Prices Change- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Palestinian Central Bureau of Statistics
